name: TERRAFORM° Four
description:
"TERRAFORM° Four" is a mixed media artwork by Lanning Sally. [2021]

The TERRAFORM° series is an ongoing reflection on our rapidly changing environment. It is a reminder to everyone that 100 multinational corporations are responsible for 71% of global greenhouse gas emissions, and that there still exists a sustainable and equitable path forward.
